Use Case 3: New Auto Policy Welcome Series

Cumulus Bank and Financial Services wants to create a three part journey to welcome new auto policy holders that introduces them to their policy and benefits.

Let's review the solution steps for this campaign.

Establish Campaign Requirements
Identify campaign goals
After a customer is added to the journey, send a welcome email to the new auto policy holder. Send a follow-up email 3 days later, and then a final email 5 days later.
The campaign is ongoing, regularly adding new customers.
Identify personalization components
The first email includes the customer’s first name, auto policy number, and start date.
The second and third emails include the customer’s first name.
Identity audience and data sources
Customers with an active auto policy created in the past 30 days.
Unified Individual, RA_PolicyInformation_02, RA_PolicyProducts, and RA_Account02 data sources.
Gather campaign materials
Create the design for the three auto policy emails in Marketing Cloud Engagement.
